                  </hi>. I produce a certificate of the prisoner's conviction (<hi rend="italic">Read: "Westminster Sessions, November,</hi> 1853; <hi rend="italic">John McGavin, Convicted of stealing a purse and</hi> 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. <hi rend="italic">
Sentenced to Four Years' Penal Servitude"</hi>)—the prisoner is the person—I have known him nine years.</p>
